# Dependencies (reinstalled inside the image)
**/node_modules

# Build outputs
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/.svelte-kit
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Tests/coverage (image is a runtime, not a dev env)
**/coverage
**/tests

# Git / editor / OS
# `.git` deliberately NOT ignored — standalone Dockerfile reads it for
# tag + SHA. Builder is multi-stage, so it never ships to runtime.
.github
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store

# Logs
**/*.log

# Project-local
plan
.claude
CLAUDE.md

# Generated assets
assets/dist
